reviewText: The guardian is the only true evil person in the show this was my favorite season of the whole series I was pissed when dal died and Ryan was taken away but it was worse when jt died on degrassi they need to make the DVDs for us Americans like they did season one and sell them every where ram ram ram

When I first saw the first season I loved this show, but then it got significantly worse from there.  The second season wasn't all that great and this season was even worse.  Sorry not all that it was cracked up to be.
I purchased this as a birthday gift for my daughter. She simply loved adding it to her growing collection. Based on her approval, I rate this at 5 stars and a huge thumbs up!!
